  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-37a55784-d4b8-4b49-9e8c-a89d0632bb3d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ED2B68F8-08DF-4DAB-A863-11C99959B753\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-82242934-044B-4405-852C-526D30754B8F\">안녕하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-EB494A54-D0F0-492C-8357-7C6E42AEC87A\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-74C5D83C-DC72-435E-A33B-A063A12AA1AA\">동작구 사당동 지하철 7호선 남성역 1번출구 앞 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9AD10702-326A-495F-9E51-1C851DC4094B\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0997083F-5DDB-4EAF-BF65-C0E754DFF098\">이수한의원입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-932B08BA-C04F-4A45-8E78-D47BB1349F2E\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8D0CBD54-10AB-455D-8BB1-006A0956DCEC\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6386D64D-2F42-45C1-B201-149C4FE3CE46\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2F1D395D-3ECF-497F-A3BF-9B1772218E47\">어느날 갑자기 심하게 어지럽고 토할 것 같아서 누워만 지내고 일어나질 못했다고 호소하는 분들이 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B67EDAA1-20AF-40DE-9DD1-AE0D13C10C10\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6293F946-7B7A-44BC-9C46-C149E78C06BB\">증세가 심한 분들은 응급실을 갈 정도로 매우 공포스럽죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-D2542F6C-CF5C-49FA-8822-3365E0E060E2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-AE853A65-BA60-4F40-87A3-74287ABE491B\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-F2ED7EF1-8D18-4BC0-A71A-1DBF5D940C63\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9B4FA752-200A-4BCD-B070-62DFEFCF68DE\">병원에서 이석증 진단을 받는 경우도 있고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-F2518F4B-3ECA-4A61-98CA-003DB7FF6F19\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-34385728-D202-4E82-9FA6-DEDFD780CE55\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-501AA3EA-F9C1-4604-BD2A-5DC4D546224C\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-92770738-19F7-42E7-9726-090D86072071\">전정신경염 진단을 받는 경우도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-697D6F2E-D81D-4CB6-BF68-6711169EE15F\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3FE9DF47-4DF8-45AA-864B-139F8E250087\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-A60DFC9E-FB37-49D5-986D-5CCBD7A23F7B\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D8DABEE4-314F-43C4-9BC5-F91D74B965D8\">이석증은 귓속에 있는 조그만 돌이 빠지는 질환으로 병명이 유명해서 많이들 알고 계시더라구요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4A4DB783-4443-4345-B6FB-A78B29EAE925\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4F516601-6759-45A3-BDE1-80FD69E3F09B\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-40332A20-38B1-4B51-872D-C580D82F0289\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2A3A3280-EA70-439B-B3AA-23446A22CD10\">반면, 전정신경염에 대해서는 모르는 분이 계셔서 간략히 소개해 드리고자 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-CA7CBB18-56DF-47B2-9C77-E04C98807B01\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-DDDEAA87-52C8-406E-AAC8-CBBC724E48C4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8cb686b4-ac30-451f-8171-8a847d48ad62\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:389px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-8cb686b4-ac30-451f-8171-8a847d48ad62\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf841ef06eeabdc6.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"389\", \"originalHeight\" : \"545\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf841ef06eeabdc6.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bf841ef06eeabdc6.png\" data-width=\"389\" data-height=\"545\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51ac233a-9298-4e3c-88e4-8982c7783d67\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-80F4C5B4-D995-45D4-B32C-9D217AAA7359\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-E973B3DE-BED7-4392-A432-3D680E2E1804\">귀는 이런 구조로 되어있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3940EC49-BF17-4439-AC9C-94FA12674D17\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-BC6D4123-3B4A-44F0-8A0F-1AB558A3D530\">귓바퀴에서 고막까지는 외이 라고 하죠</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-F39EE59C-1CFC-4668-AFA9-55B266469C7F\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-E3B5CDF8-A94D-4B17-AD17-95AD1F5257A8\">고막에서 반고리관 전까지를 중이,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-22A07684-B978-48B6-9483-A8CD7025A245\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4EB02471-665B-4F7B-9FFA-4834DEE608D9\">그보다 더 안쪽을 내이 라고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-70E48146-6B70-4C33-9EFF-19242E2B3BFC\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-859605E9-2B3F-4DE2-AF69-9CBE56FA7C15\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-07128309-829A-45D7-9EF2-E794BCA35E13\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-AD8D0A9E-BC7D-4ACE-BBF5-7F1EA1E32FF8\">이석증과 전정신경염은 둘 다 &#x27;내이&#x27;에 병이 생긴겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-57A8C9D6-2A71-40CB-A2B2-3D1A838F1291\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-B45E3451-DD2F-4194-AAB1-275D99CE912B\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5102A7BD-C383-40DD-9D33-72B257EADF30\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-FF30B826-EC4D-4E88-A575-3939CE3EB344\">이석증은 반고리관에서, 전정신경염은 그 주변 신경에서 문제가 발생하죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-DE606CCB-A913-4734-AEB7-25B52B63D824\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-C883A3E4-45BB-4442-BA61-FCB0DFFB95C9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0d9a0a78-d201-49b8-a79b-c232ab89e22b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0d9a0a78-d201-49b8-a79b-c232ab89e22b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4fec4cf0c40f48d2.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2480\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3507\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4fec4cf0c40f48d2.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4fec4cf0c40f48d2.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bcc6d776-df49-4971-ae95-178cd5e32533\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-29FB0167-C4BB-4E67-B100-08B0603AEF93\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-AC2CFD2D-8CFF-410D-B005-13A7E9D5F5DC\">주 원인이 면역력 저하로 인한 감염이나 혈액순환 장애이기에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5D1CA2AA-D887-4533-99A0-BD7B17B97730\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D9837B41-4B30-4838-B45F-C339F8C45B20\">전정신경의 염증을 치료하는 것 뿐 아니라, 근본 원인에 맞는 치료를 해줘야합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8AE12DC6-60D7-4C59-A008-9A52ABBF47E9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3F0FFB04-9F64-442E-A31C-85AC7AA031A8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-CCF7032B-22EA-4F71-AFB2-3C3FE93CF33A\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D8D11093-D9F2-475C-9511-7B6BB9FA6523\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E95B6A88-B2DA-40D7-9392-BED7224C392D\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2D49D365-378D-4406-B98A-2BB7B696999F\">전정신경염 증상이 있으시면 이수한의원에서 진료받으세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-t